  "title": "Writer",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Creative Writer / Scriptwriter – Video Production</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Overview:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p> Join our vibrant video production house as a Creative Writer, where storytelling meets moving visuals. You’ll craft compelling scripts, punchy dialogue, and emotionally resonant narratives that elevate brands, spark conversations, and captivate audiences across platforms.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>What you’ll do:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop original concepts and structured scripts for short-form videos, promotional spots, and branded content.</li>\n  <li>Write clear, engaging, and on-brand dialogue with strong character voices.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with producers, directors, and editors to shape tone, pacing, and storytelling arcs. -Conduct rapid research, outline scenes, and deliver reusable script templates for efficiency. -Revise based on feedback, ensuring timely delivery without sacrificing quality.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>What we’re looking for:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong portfolio showcasing scriptwriting for video or multimedia (concepts, dialogue, narratives).</li>\n  <li>Proficiency with script formats and beat sheets; ability to adapt to different genres and brands.</li>\n  <li>Excellent writing, editing, and storytelling instincts; collaborative spirit.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under tight deadlines and manage multiple projects.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>- Bachelor's Degree in English, Creative Writing, Journalism or related field</p>\n<p>Talented fresh graduates are welcome to apply</p>",
